{"tid":1495494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818街訪：如果你中左六合彩，你會點用筆錢？","createTime":"2019-08-22T05:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:01:39.000Z","uid":157616,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92abe48c3f25e033c190eb140b77840050b7db39","tid":1495494,"uid":157616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"[借Account 代post]<br />\n大家好，小女子最近整左個飲食channel，但係呢幾個月香港發生嘅事，令我覺得不得不出聲，所以我就同朋友整咗呢條片關於反送中人仕，幫手文宣，問佢地一條問題- 如果中左六合彩既話，你地會點用筆錢？<br />\n每問一個人，我都想喊；無人個想自己被捕或者見到朋友被捕，面對被捕，心理壓力大，金錢壓力亦都唔細。<br />\n錢，對於每一個香港人都很重要，尤其係面對司法程序既人。<br />\n我本以為好多人會想離開這個日趨惡劣的地方，但原來每個人都愛呢個地方。<br />\n香港最美麗並不是經濟，而是人。<br />\n成日啲人都話香港人無情，無愛心，但係今次訪問，佢哋嗰個有情有義，唔會因為有錢就離開香港呢個家。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家可以既話希望subscribe 我啦，我遲下應該會去撐警集會，問返同一條問題。<br />\n謝謝你們。<br />\n<br />\n初初整片，希望大家俾啲意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnx6cf2188k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drnx6cf2188k&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGISK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=728bd00f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnx6cf2188k</a>"},{"pid":"683e901e5ade0f08f4bc77d5adf6ca435fc1f33f","tid":1495494,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU，而家搭車犯法呀?</strong></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yrRtRqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyrRtRqw.jpg&h=a938cd9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCkHxb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwT